high_descs: Turn around and face the white cabinet with a tissue box on it.
Pick the soap up from the white cabinet.
Put the soap in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the soap up again.
Turn to the right to face the white cabinet.
Put the soap on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right at the sink and walk to the white dresser.
Pick up the bar of soap on the left side of the dresser.
Turn left to face the sink.
Put the bar of soap inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the white dresser on the left.
Put the rinsed bar of soap on the right side of the dresser in front of the pink bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a dresser.

high_descs: Turn right and face the white cabinet.
Pick up the bar of soap on the cabinet.
Turn left and face the sink.
Place the soap on the cabinet, on the right side, in front of the pink soap container.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a cabinet.
